rows.label: tlk45310341_02_msg0001
rows.name:
The Hræsvelgr Mercenaries take on
jobs anywhere in Alst.

rows.label: tlk45310341_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Me and my sister joined up after
Vandham saved our asses on a
mission one time.

rows.label: tlk45310341_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I still haven't come close to paying
him back for that...

rows.label: tlk45310341_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Never dreamed he'd be gone
before I got the chance.

rows.label: tlk45310341_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Zuo and Yuu are working hard to pick
up the slack, but who knows what'll
become of the Hræsvelgr Mercenaries...
